doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    title #{title}
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='IE=edge,chrome=1')
    meta(name='description', content='Save your Manga info')
    meta(name='author', content='Rafase282')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    link(rel='shortcut icon', href='https://manga-client.herokuapp.com/images/favicon.ico')
    link(rel='apple-touch-icon', href='https://manga-client.herokuapp.com/images/favicon.ico')
    link(rel='stylesheet prefetch', href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/normalize/3.0.3/normalize.min.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet prefetch', href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Titillium+Web: 400, 700')
    link(rel='stylesheet prefetch', href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.97.6/css/materialize.min.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet prefetch', href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.5.0/css/font-awesome.min.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet prefetch', href='https://mangadb-front-rafase282.c9users.io/stylesheets/main.css')
    script(type='text/javascript').
      var token = '#{token}';
      var user = '#{user}';
      var api = '#{api}';
  body
    nav
      .nav-wrapper.light-blue.darken-4
        a.brand-logo(href='/') MangaDB
        ul.right.hide-on-med-and-down
          if user
            li
              a(href=url)
                i.material-icons.left verified_user
                | #{user}
            li
              a(href='/logout')
                i.material-icons.left hot_tub
                | Logout
          else
            li
              a(href='/signup')
                i.material-icons.left face
                | Sign Up
            li
              a(href='/login')
                i.material-icons.left lock_open
                | Log In
    .container
      if msg.error && msg.error.length
        .center-align.valign-wrapper.red.accent-3
          div.valign.flow-text= msg.error
      if msg.info && msg.info.length
        .center-align.valign-wrapper.blue.darken-1
          div.valign.flow-text= msg.info
      if msg.success && msg.success.length
        .center-align.valign-wrapper.green.accent-2
          div.valign.flow-text= msg.success
    block content

    footer.page-footer.center-align.light-blue.darken-4
      .container
        .row
          .col.l6.s12
            h5.white-text About the Site
            p.grey-text.text-lighten-4
              | The Project is divided in two parts, the&nbsp;
              a.grey-text(href='https://github.com/Rafase282/mangadb', taget='_blank') Core API&nbsp;
              | which has the core functionalities like databases, account and manga handling and more, and the&nbsp;
              a.grey-text(href='https://github.com/Rafase282/mangadb-front', taget='_blank') Client's App.&nbsp;
              | which is what you can see and interact with.
              | Created and designed by&nbsp;
              a.grey-text(href='https://gitter.im/Rafase282', taget='_blank') Rafase282
              | &nbsp;using&nbsp;
              a.grey-text(href='http://materializecss.com/', taget='_blank') Materialize&nbsp
              | Project's chatroom via gitter at&nbsp
              a.grey-text(href='https://gitter.im/Rafase282/Mangadb', taget='_blank') MangaDB&nbsp
            p.grey-text.text-lighten-4
              | Pull request are with improvements or new features are welcome but the author reserves the rights to accept or reject at will.&nbsp;
              | If you encounter an issue with the way the page is displayed, forms or anything UX related please open an issue on the&nbsp;
              a.grey-text(href='https://github.com/Rafase282/mangadb-front/issues', taget='_blank') Client's Issue Tracker.&nbsp;
              | For issues with the
              | functionality such as account problems, manga issues then use the&nbsp;
              a.grey-text(href='https://github.com/Rafase282/mangadb/issues', taget='_blank') API's Issue Tracker.
          .col.l4.offset-l2.s12
            h5.white-text Contact Me
            .col.s6
              ul.white-text
                li
                  a(href='mailto:rafase282@gmail.com')
                    i.fa.fa-envelope.fa-fw
                  | &nbsp;E-Mail
                li
                  a(href='https://github.com/Rafase282', target='_blank')
                    i.fa.fa-github.fa-fw
                  | &nbsp;Github
                li
                  a(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/rafase282', target='_blank')
                    i.fa.fa-linkedin
                  | &nbsp;LinkedIn
            .col.s6
              ul.white-text
                li
                  a(href='http://codepen.io/Rafase282', target='_blank')
                    i.fa.fa-codepen
                  | &nbsp;Codepen
                li
                  a(href='https://rafase282.wordpress.com/', target='_blank')
                    i.fa.fa-wordpress
                  | &nbsp;Wordpress
                li
                  a(href='http://www.freecodecamp.com/rafase282', target='_blank')
                    | (
                    i.fa.fa-fire.fa-fw
                    | )
                  | &nbsp;FreeCodeCamp
